# Pluto Labs — New App Rule

**Read `AGENTS.md` in the repo root before implementing.**

## Quick checklist

1. Create `src/apps/<kebab-name>/` with default-export component + colocated CSS
2. Extract pure logic to `*Logic.ts` when state is non-trivial
3. Register lazy import + `AppEntry` in `src/registry/apps.ts` only — never edit `App.tsx`
4. No custom header/back button — `AppShell` handles chrome
5. Use CSS variables from `src/index.css` (dark flat theme, no neon)
6. Game entrance animations: run on load/new-game key only, not every move
7. Canvas games: `useRef` game state + `requestAnimationFrame`, not per-frame `setState`
8. Run `npm run build` and fix TypeScript errors

## Registry entry shape

```typescript
{
  id: "my-app",
  title: "My App",
  description: "Short catalog description.",
  category: "tool", // tool | game | experiment
  route: "/apps/my-app",
  accent: "cyan",   // cyan | magenta | purple | green
  icon: "◆",
  tags: ["utility"],
  component: MyApp,
}
```
